What We Offer?

  • State-of-the-Art Kitchen Facilities centrally located in multiple Pune locations.
  • Implementation of FSSAI Standard Audit Procedures.
  • Management Team boasting decades of experience in Corporate Catering.
  • Adherence to ISO-22000 Standards.
  • In-House Quality Control Team for stringent quality checks.
  • Appointment of a Dedicated Site Manager for seamless coordination.
  • Cafeteria Management
  • In House Cooking
  • Multi-Cuisine Menu Banks
  • Packed Meals
  • Pop-Up Counters
  • Tuck Shops
  • Festival Menus
  • Event Catering

Challenges & Solutions

  • Food delivery getting delayed ‚Üí Live Tracking of the food preparation
  • Foreign objects in the food ‚Üí Sanitizing and Sorting
  • Monotonous Menu ‚Üí Multi-cuisine Menu Bank
  • Food Contamination ‚Üí Segregation of Raw Material
  • Food Spoilage Due to Temperature ‚Üí Temperature Records and Insulated Packing
  • Food Borne Illness ‚Üí Regular water and food testing, adherence to PPE standards, and staff medical check-ups.

Operation Cycle

Hiring ‚Üí Purchasing ‚Üí Receiving ‚Üí Sanitizing ‚Üí Storing ‚Üí Processing ‚Üí Quality Testing ‚Üí Packing ‚Üí Dispatch ‚Üí Transport ‚Üí Serving ‚Üí Windup

Kitchen Design

  • Compliant Designs with FSSAI Audit Standards
  • Tailored to Cater to the High Meal Demand of 5000 Meals Daily
  • Segmented into Various Sections: Receiving, Dry Store, Cold Store, Veg Prep, Non-Veg Prep, Wet Grinding, Frying, Boiling, Veg/Non-Veg Cooking, Chapati, Packing, Dispatch
  • Equipped with Spacious Cold Rooms and Generator Backup
